#: .\effects.json
msgid "Wasted"
msgstr "爛醉如泥"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Wasted'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You tried 'Uncle Ben's Mustang' moonshine. You feel like you died, "
"resurrected and then died again."
msgstr "你嘗試了'本叔叔的野馬'私釀酒。感覺像是死了一次，復活後又死了一次。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Wasted'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You feel AWFUL."
msgstr "你感覺糟透了。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Teach"
msgstr "傳授"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Teach'.
#: .\effects.json
