msgstr "你感到力量充沛。"

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Waiting"
msgstr "等待中"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Waiting'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "This NPC is waiting for something."
msgstr "這個NPC正在等待某事。"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Wandering Masters"
msgstr "流浪大師"

#. ~ Description for Wandering Masters
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Mod adds 'Wandering Masters', NPCs that can 'teach' player martial arts after completing their quest line.\n"
"Check mod folder for more information."
msgstr ""
"此模組添加了'流浪大師'，這些NPC在完成其任務線後可以'傳授'玩家武術。\n"
"查看模組文件夾獲取更多信息。"

