#: .\monsters\quest_monsters.json
msgid ""
"Apparently this zombie was doing time when the Cataclysm struck.  It wears "
"black and white striped prisoner clothes, and tattoos can be seen on his "
"decaying skin. One of the tatoos on his face looks like a dragon."
msgstr "顯然，這隻殭屍在災變發生時正在服刑。它穿著黑白條紋的囚服，腐爛的皮膚上可見紋身。它臉上的一個紋身看起來像一條龍。"

#: .\monsters\quest_monsters.json
msgid ""
"A human body covered by a weather-beaten and badly damaged set of riot gear."
" This one has a wooden hand."
msgstr "一具覆蓋著飽經風霜且嚴重破損的防暴裝備的人體。這隻殭屍有一隻木製的手。"

#: .\monsters\turret.json
msgid "M240 autonomous CROWS II ml"
msgid_plural "M240 autonomous CROWS II mls"
msgstr[0] "M240自主CROWS II ml"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'M240 autonomous CROWS II ml'}
#: .\monsters\turret.json
msgid ""
"A remote weapon system derived from the M153 CROWS II and enhanced with "
"autonomous operation software.  Thousands of these were deployed by the US "
"military before the Cataclysm and they were valued for their use in engaging"
" infantry without exposing the operator.  This one is fitted with a M240."
msgstr ""
"一種源自M153 CROWS "
"II並增強自主操作軟件的遠程武器系統。災變前美軍部署了數千臺，因其能在不暴露操作員的情況下攻擊步兵而備受重視。這臺配備了M240。"

