#: .\npc\Teachers\wanderer_knight.json
msgid "About that job…"
msgstr "關於那個工作……"

#: .\npc\Flame Knuckle\Flame_Knuckle_Leader.json
#: .\npc\Moneylender_hub\hobo.json .\npc\Moneylender_hub\moneylender.json
#: .\npc\Refugee center\NPC_Barry_Button.json center\NPC_Berry_Button.json
